<document>
  <properties>
    <title>ECM Website Development</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="The JSP tag library">
      <subsection name="Importing the taglib">
        <p>The taglib definition file is present as <code>/META-INF/hst.tld</code> within the
          included HST jar file (see <a href="include.html">include the HST</a>) and should be found
          by your web application. The URI of the taglib is
          <code>http://www.hippoecm.org/jsp/hst</code> so to import the taglib in your jsp use the
          piece of code below. As prefix we recommend <code>hst</code>, as a simple <code>h</code>
          is commonly used for jsf html tags.</p>
        <source><![CDATA[<%@ taglib uri="http://www.hippoecm.org/jsp/hst" prefix="hst" %>]]></source>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Tags">
        <p>The following tags are available:</p>
        <table cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">
          <tr><th>Tag</th><th>Decription</th></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:content&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Gets the value of a property from a context object.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:context&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Creates a new context objects from an existing one and a location.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:include&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Includes in the page the output for a certain repository location, as found via
              the URL mapping functionality.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:encodeURL&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Encodes a repository path location to a URL valid for URL mapping.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:documents&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a list of documents.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:articles&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a list of articles.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:news&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a list of news items.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:events&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a list of events.</td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:menu&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a dynamic menu as read from content in the repository.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><pre>&lt;hst:siteMap&gt;</pre></td>
            <td>Shows a dynamic site map as read from content in the repository.</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p>No extensive documentation is available as the taglib is under development.</p>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>
